uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.hbasestore

Class HBaseProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store.StoreProperties
      • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.hbasestore.HBaseProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class HBaseProperties
extends StoreProperties
    HBaseProperties contains specific configuration information for the hbase store, such as database connection strings. It wraps Properties and lazy loads the all properties from a file when first used.
